   ROA = Net Income / Total Assets × 100%

4) **Operating Cash Flow to Net Income Ratio**
   Operating Cash Flow to Net Income Ratio = Net Cash Flow from Operating Activities / Net Income
   Operating Cash Flow to Net Income Ratio = -4,504,752.68 / 111,731.83 = -40.32

5) **Net Profit Margin**
   Net Profit Margin = Net Income / Total Revenue × 100%
   Net Profit Margin = 111,731.83 / 791,992.51 × 100% = 14.11%

6) **Gross Profit Margin**
   Gross Profit Margin = Gross Profit / Total Revenue × 100%
   Gross Profit Margin = 287,062.51 / 791,992.51 × 100% = 36.25%
